Germany’s Top Court to Hear Euro-Fund Cases Soon, Spiegel Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-06-13T16:40:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-13/germany-s-top-court-to-hear-euro-fund-cases-soon-spiegel-says.html
Germany ’s constitutional court will
hear a complaint against the Greek bailout and the euro-area
rescue fund soon and allow bailouts only under some conditions,
 Der Spiegel  magazine reported today, citing remarks by Andreas Vosskuhle, the court’s chief justice.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 